title: Latest news & NFC West rosters
itunes:title: Latest news & NFC West rosters
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling -- are joined by special co-host Colleen Wolfe to discuss the latest NFL news including Geno Smith and the Jets QB position (5:13). The guys then hit roster reset on the NFC West (19:53), remember their first music concert experiences (34:15) before discussing Wess' "Ohio River Offense" article (44:26).
